data.title: LEGENDS 1027 WLGZ
data.meta_description: The Biggest Hits in the History of the World!  The greatest songs from the 60s, 70s, and 80s, including The Jackson Five, The Bee Gees, Buble, Elvis, The Carpenters, Diamond, Dion, Abba, The Beatles, Donna Summer, Chicago, The Four Seasons, Springsteen, James Brown, and The Rolling Stones.  Arguably the most popular music station in all of Rochester, there is nothing like Legends 102.7, WLGZ
